Mix cream cheese and tandoori paste in medium bowl. Add chicken; toss to coat. Refrigerate 30 min. to marinate. Heat broiler. Remove chicken from marinade; reserve marinade. Thread chicken onto 4 skewers; brush with reserved marinade. Place on rack of broiler pan. Broil, 6 inches from heat, 8 to 10 min. or until chicken is done, turning after 5 min.